description: I´ve stopped by the bus stop and switched on my camera. One short walk around was enough to find someone willing to talk with me on camera. A young man who was a student of Physical Education faculty here in Prague. Therefore I knew that his body will be totally worthy. His friendly attitude, cute eyes and funny haircut have been the right attributes that we all like about Czech Hunter. Even tough I´ve made many videos, there is one thing which amaze me every time. The willingness to do basically everything in public. Once you mix that with good money you have absolute freedom here in Prague. So Gents if you are thinking about your next holidays, I recommend you to put Prague on the top of your list. See you in a week!
title: Czech Hunter 141
